item.description:
Valid columns are:
 name: Tag name series: Number of series in the tag.  When no columns are provided the default is used. (name)
Examples # View all tags list tags # View tags and the number of series tagged list tags name, series # sample output (list tags) { &quot;columns&quot;: [&quot;name&quot;, &quot;series&quot;], &quot;tags&quot;: [ [&quot;linux&quot;, 52042], [&quot;windows&quot;, 7] ] }
